data.description: Fantastic 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath home! Warm wall tones and art niches throughout. Upgraded kitchen is complete with maple cabinets, granite countertops, breakfast bar, and stainless steel appliances. Large master suite located downstairs has plush carpet with ceiling fan and bay window. Full spa like bathroom with double sink vanity and separate soaking tub + shower. Spacious walk in closet! Huge great room and living room with vaulted ceilings. Oversized backyard features a covered patio with desert landscaping and plenty of room for entertaining! This home is sure to go quick, so come see it today before it''s too late!
